5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Doolandella"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Doolandella? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Doolandella, Forest Lake, Pallara and Inala. Our 5-star instructors help Doolandella students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Doolandella is a rapidly growing outer-southwestern suburb characterized by brand-new master-planned housing estates interspersed with older acreage remnants. This dual character provides a superb learning environment: the wide, perfectly gridded new estate roads are exceptional for foundational car control, while the surrounding established arterial corridors like Blunder Road offer advanced, multi-lane traffic practice."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"Our instructors use Doolandella's evolving infrastructure strategically. Learners master basic maneuvers in the quiet modern estates before progressively moving toward the major commercial hubs of Forest Lake and Inala. This smooth transition from quiet backstreets to high-density traffic perfectly prepares students for the practical assessment at Sherwood."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Doolandella learners test at the Sherwood TMR Customer Service Centre. Free pickup from Doolandella, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5"